description:
In this video, we're giving you a special karaoke "White Christmas" (Key : C)! Check it out and enjoy the festive season!
This year, instead of staying in on Christmas Eve, why not celebrate the holiday in style with a White Christmas "Karaoke" video! We've got all the hits covered, and we're even throwing in a special surprise for the end! So put on your most festive outfit and celebrate the season with us!

Songwriters: Irving Berlin
Motion Graphics Used : NOYA STUDIO - THE KING OF MOTION GRAPHICS https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKJh...
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters  youtube production!
